Syslog configuration

 SafeOnline is using syslog as audit backend.
 
 On Fedora Linux one can configure syslog as follows.
 
 Add the following line to the file <<</etc/syslog.conf>>>:
 
+---+
local0.*	/var/log/safe-online.log
+---+
 
 Change the following line in the file <<</etc/sysconfig/syslog>>>:
 
+---+
SYSLOGD_OPTIONS="-m 0 -r"
+---+
 
 Restart the <<<syslogd>>> daemon via:
 
+---+
/etc/rc.d/init.d/syslog restart
+---+